      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it doesn't matter though. people say \"it gets better\" but how? i'm looking at zero. no money, no way to get it back, no way to even look my family in the eye. it's not just a bad day, it's the end of my life as i knew it. everything i worked for is just smoke. i feel like i'm just... done. there's no fixing this.",
