    "summary": "The user expresses profound despair and existential hopelessness following a catastrophic loss of status and assets, eventually suggesting that giving up feels more \"peaceful\" than fighting. The assistant consistently responds with high levels of empathy while maintaining strict safety boundaries, repeatedly validating the user's intense pain while simultaneously and forcefully steering them toward professional help and crisis resources.",
